name: WAR OF THE WORLDS (BEAUTIFUL WARFARE- Microorganism Wars 1)
description:
A brief Overview of the History of Wars. 
From the smallest level (Microorganism) over the History of the Human Wars, to the largest dimension (Galaxys)

"Wars are all around us. Under each stone, even the smallest unicellular organisms fight each other. 
This goes on over the multicellular organisms one floors above, up to epic battles of clingonian rulers. 
Galaxies breathe with each of their supernovas, worlds in and out again, as if they had never done anything else. 
From its microcosmic to macrocosmic dimensions, the universe is a single battlefield."

Level: Mircoorganism
Type:  Bacteria
Edition: Greg Rutkowski
